@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FAQ";
}

<div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq-header">
        <h2 class="page-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="faq-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about carpooling with Carvisto</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-card">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>What is carpooling?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Carpooling is a shared transportation arrangement where multiple people travel together in one vehicle.
                    The driver offers empty seats in their car to passengers traveling in the same direction, sharing the costs of the journey.
                    This practice reduces traffic congestion, lowers transportation costs, and helps reduce environmental impact.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>How does Carvisto work?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Carvisto connects drivers with empty seats to passengers traveling in the same direction.
                    Drivers can create trips by specifying their route, departure time, vehicle details, and price per seat.
                    Passengers can search for available trips, view driver profiles, and book seats.
                    The platform facilitates the entire process from finding a ride to completing the journey.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>How do I create a trip as a driver?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>To create a trip as a driver:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Log in to your Carvisto account</li>
                    <li>Navigate to "My Account" and click "Create New Trip"</li>
                    <li>Fill in the required details: departure and arrival locations, date and time, price per seat, and vehicle information</li>
                    <li>Add any additional information or requirements for passengers</li>
                    <li>Click "Create Trip" to publish your journey</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Your trip will then be visible to potential passengers searching for rides on that route.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>How do I book a trip as a passenger?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>To book a trip as a passenger:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Search for available trips by entering your departure and destination locations</li>
                    <li>Browse the list of available trips matching your criteria</li>
                    <li>Click on a trip to view its details and the driver's profile</li>
                    <li>Click the "Book" button to reserve your seat</li>
                    <li>Confirm your booking and complete any required payment</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Once booked, you'll receive the driver's contact information and trip details.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>How is the price determined?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Prices are set by drivers based on factors such as:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Distance of the journey</li>
                    <li>Fuel costs</li>
                    <li>Toll fees</li>
                    <li>Vehicle maintenance</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Carvisto encourages fair pricing that makes carpooling beneficial for both drivers and passengers.
                    The goal is to share travel costs, not to generate profit.As a guideline, prices typically cover
                    the driver's expenses while offering passengers a more affordable alternative to other transportation options.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>Is carpooling safe?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Carvisto prioritizes safety through several measures:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>User verification and profile reviews</li>
                    <li>Rating system for both drivers and passengers</li>
                    <li>Ability to view driver profiles and vehicle information before booking</li>
                    <li>Secure messaging system within the platform</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We recommend users to check ratings and reviews, communicate clearly about meeting points,
                    and share trip details with a trusted contact before departure. Always trust your instincts and
                    cancel if you feel uncomfortable with any arrangement.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>What are the benefits of carpooling?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Carpooling offers numerous benefits:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Cost savings:</strong> Share fuel, toll, and parking costs</li>
                    <li><strong>Environmental impact:</strong> Reduce carbon emissions by having fewer cars on the road</li>
                    <li><strong>Reduced traffic:</strong> Help decrease congestion during peak hours</li>
                    <li><strong>Social interaction:</strong> Meet new people and make connections</li>
                    <li><strong>Reduced stress:</strong> Share driving responsibilities on long journeys</li>
                    <li><strong>Access to HOV lanes:</strong> In many areas, carpooling vehicles can use dedicated lanes</li>
                </ul>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
                <h3>Can I cancel my trip or booking?</h3>
                <div class="faq-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, both drivers and passengers can cancel trips, but we encourage responsible use of this feature:</p>
                <p><strong>For drivers:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>You can cancel a trip through your account dashboard</li>
                    <li>All passengers will be notified automatically</li>
                    <li>Frequent cancellations may affect your driver rating</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>For passengers:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>You can cancel your booking through your account dashboard</li>
                    <li>The driver will be notified of your cancellation</li>
                    <li>Last-minute cancellations may affect your passenger rating</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We recommend cancelling as early as possible to allow drivers and passengers to make alternative arrangements.</p>
                <p>ㅤ</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    function toggleAnswer(element) {
        const item = element.parentElement;
        const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
        const icon = item.querySelector('.faq-icon svg');
        
        if (answer.style.maxHeight) {
            answer.style.maxHeight = null;
            icon.innerHTML = '<path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"/>';
        } else {
            answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + "px";
            icon.innerHTML = '<path d="M4 8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h7a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-7A.5.5 0 0 1 4 8"/>';
        }
    }
</script>
